---
---

<section class="our-story">
  <div class="story-container container">
    <div class="story-grid">
      <div class="story-text-col">
        <span class="story-eyebrow">Nuestra Historia</span>
        <h2 class="story-title">
          Más de una década<br />formando<br />
          <span class="story-highlight">paracaidistas</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="story-body">
          <p>
            Skydive Inka Perú (SKIP), con más de una década de operación continua, es una asociación aero-deportiva especializada en paracaidismo, con la mayor trayectoria operativa reciente en el país.
          </p>
          <p>
            Desde su reconocimiento formal en 2014 por la Dirección General de Aeronáutica Civil (DGAC) del Ministerio de Transportes y Comunicaciones, opera bajo estándares regulados de seguridad y entrenamiento.
          </p>
          <p>
            SKIP constituye un eje técnico dentro de la comunidad aerodeportiva nacional, consolidándose como una institución de referencia para la práctica del paracaidismo deportivo estructurado y continuo.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="story-signature">
          <img src="/images/isotipo-skip.svg" alt="" class="story-signature-logo" aria-hidden="true" />
          <div class="story-signature-text">
            <span class="signature-name">Reconocidos por DGAC</span>
            <span class="signature-role">RD N° 076-2014-MTC/12</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="story-images-col">
        <div class="story-img-main">
          <img src="/images/FOTO_2INSTRUCTORES.webp" alt="Instructores de Skydive Inka Perú" />
          <div class="story-img-badge">
            <span class="badge-year">2014</span>
            <span class="badge-text">Reconocidos por DGAC</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="story-img-secondary">
          <img src="/images/paracaidista-video.png" alt="Paracaidista en vuelo" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .our-story {
    background-color: var(--white);
    padding: var(--section-padding) 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .story-container {
    max-width: var(--container-max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--container-padding-x);
  }

  .story-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .story-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: var(--primary-blue);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 40px;
  }

  .story-eyebrow::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 50%;
    width: 28px;
    height: 2px;
    background-color: var(--primary-blue);
  }

  .story-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 52px);
    line-height: 1;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .story-highlight {
    color: var(--primary-blue);
    display: inline-block;
    position: relative;
  }

  .story-highlight::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 8px;
    background-color: var(--primary-light);
    opacity: 0.3;
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .story-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .story-body p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--gray-text);
  }

  .story-body p:first-child::first-letter {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 48px;
    float: left;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-right: 8px;
    margin-top: 4px;
    color: var(--primary-blue);
  }

  .story-signature {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    padding-top: 24px;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--gray-light);
  }

  .story-signature-logo {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
  }

  .story-signature-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .signature-name {
    font-family: var(--font-header);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .signature-role {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gray-medium);
  }

  .story-img-main {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .story-img-main img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 420px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .story-img-badge {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -16px;
    right: -16px;
    background-color: var(--primary-blue);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    padding: 16px 24px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .badge-year {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 28px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .badge-text {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 10px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .story-img-secondary {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 40px;
  }

  .story-img-secondary img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 220px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .story-img-secondary::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    width: 4px;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: var(--accent-gold);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .story-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 48px;
    }

    .story-img-main img {
      height: 320px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .our-story {
      padding: 48px 0;
    }

    .story-img-badge {
      bottom: -12px;
      right: 12px;
      padding: 12px 18px;
    }

    .badge-year {
      font-size: 22px;
    }

    .story-img-secondary {
      padding-left: 24px;
    }

    .story-img-secondary img {
      height: 180px;
    }
  }
</style>
